{
  "stem": "21008.3",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "He had to prove that his wife was Aryan.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And then they released him.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "OK, so on that February 27, we went to my grandparents', and we stayed there for a week.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And as I said, we heard that Jews from mixed marriages were released.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And after a week we went back home into our own apartment, and nothing was disturbed.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And-- I should mention also that we had to have a star with the word 'Jude' on it on our front door.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And on the apartment door, also, you had to have that.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "But anyway, nothing was disturbed.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And we came home.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And we were there for about an hour, and the bell rang.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "The Gestapo came to arrest Rosalita Lehmann-- me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they arrested me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They took me with them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I was for four days also in that same Gestapo prison, a converted old age home, and I had to prove that my mother is a Aryan.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And after I had done this with all the papers I had, my mother gave me, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I was released.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But, I mean, I hear my mother still screaming when they took me away.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, I was 15 years old.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And these guys take her daughter away, you know.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I came back.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were just not treated at all.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were just on the floor in hallways, you know.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was overcrowded.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't remember getting food or anything.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "My mother had given me a piece of bread to take along, which I didn't eat, because when I was finally released on one of the lower floors in the old age home, there was behind a gate that was closed off was my girlfriend of mine calling me, calling my name.",
      "word_count": 52
    }
  ],
